<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Our Newsletter</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px;">
    <h1 style="color: #2c3e50;">Welcome to {{appName}} Newsletter!</h1>
    
    <div style="background-color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 20px;">
      <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for subscribing to our newsletter! You'll now receive updates about:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>New training courses and resources</li>
        <li>Latest AI tools and technologies</li>
        <li>Exclusive content and insights</li>
        <li>Community updates and events</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>We're excited to have you on board!</p>
      
      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
        <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}" style="background-color: #e74c3c; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;">
          Unsubscribe
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #7f8c8d;">
      If you did not subscribe to this newsletter, please ignore this email.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

